-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">3.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Undang-Undang Nomor 29 tahun 2007 tentang Pemerintahan Provinsi Daerah Khusus Ibukota Jakarta sebagai Ibukota Negara Kesatuan Republik Indonesia;</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"font-size: 5px;\" colspan=\"7\"><span>&nbsp;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"4\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"21\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">4.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Peraturan Menteri Tenaga Kerja dan Transmigrasi RI Nomor PER.02/MEN/III/2008 Tanggal 21 April 2008 tentang Tata Cara Penggunaan Tenaga Kerja Asing;</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"font-size: 5px;\" colspan=\"7\"><span>&nbsp;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"4\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"21\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">5.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Peraturan Daerah Provinsi DKI Jakarta Nomor 6 tahun 2004 tentang Ketenagakerjaan;</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"font-size: 5px;\" colspan=\"7\"><span>&nbsp;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"4\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span