P ini dilarang digunakan untuk melakukan :</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"36\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">a.</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"8\" valign=\"top\" width=\"684\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Kegiatan usaha perdagangan yang tidak sesuai dengan kelembagaan dan/atau kegiatan usaha, sebagaimana yang tercantum di dalam SIUP;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"36\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">b.</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"8\" valign=\"top\" width=\"684\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Kegiatan usaha yang mengaku kegiatan perdagangan, untuk menghimpun dana dari masyarakat dengan menawarkan janji keuntungan yang tidak wajar (money game); atau</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"36\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">c.</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"8\" valign=\"top\" width=\"684\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Kegiatan usaha perdagangan lainnya (selain butir a dan b) yang telah diatur melalui ketentuan peraturan perundang-undangan tersendiri.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"8\" valign=\"top\" width=\"720\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" width=\"90\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Dikeluarkan di</span></td>\r\n<td width=\"10\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">:</span></td>\r\n<td width=\"200\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Jakarta</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" width=\"90\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Pada tanggal</span></td>\r\n<td width=\"10\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">:</span></td>\r\n<td width=\"200\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">{tanggal_sekarang}</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" width=\"90\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Pendaftaran ulang tanggal</span></td>\r\n<td width=\"10\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">:</span></td>\r\n<td width=\"200\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"8\" valign=\"top\" width=\"720\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" colspan=\"5\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">KEPALA KANTOR</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" colspan=\"5\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">PELAYANAN TERPADU SATU PINTU</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" colspan=\"5\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">{namawil}</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\">{qrcode}</td>\r\n<td width=\"50\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\">foto 3x4</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" colspan=\"5\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">{nm_kepala}</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" colspan=\"5\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">NIP. {nip_kepala}</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','dokizin1320150311035727.docx','Y'),
